by the same company?

319
00:24:56,495 --> 00:24:57,662
I think so.

320
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,708
By the way...

321
00:25:03,126 --> 00:25:04,711
I wonder why I feel...

322
00:25:06,254 --> 00:25:07,380
so agitated by this painting.

323
00:25:09,799 --> 00:25:11,801
The painting looks similar
to the company logo.

324
00:25:13,011 --> 00:25:16,056
But the title of the painting
looks like a weird code.

325
00:25:16,640 --> 00:25:18,475
BY HUI WON

326
00:25:31,446 --> 00:25:32,948
THE CATEGORY OF MEDICINE AND BIOETHICS

327
00:25:44,417 --> 00:25:46,461
