00:26:07,023 --> 00:26:09,234
WRITTEN AT HUIWONJAE
AS I WAIT FOR SPRING TO COME

332
00:26:12,862 --> 00:26:14,739
HUI WON

333
00:26:16,825 --> 00:26:20,161
WRITTEN AT HUIWONJAE
AS I WAIT FOR SPRING TO COME - LEE WON-GIL

334
00:27:32,567 --> 00:27:35,320
Was that the doctor who just left?

335
00:27:35,779 --> 00:27:36,780
Yes.

336
00:27:37,781 --> 00:27:40,200
He finally has the output.

337
00:27:41,117 --> 00:27:42,160
Does he?

338
00:27:42,243 --> 00:27:48,625
Humans think pain is their worst enemy
and fear in life.

339
00:27:49,209 --> 00:27:52,420
But the pain is what makes us
fight and achieve.

340
00:27:53,088 --> 00:27:54,130
Right.

341
00:27:54,839 --> 00:27:57,884
At the end of the dreadful pain,
I found it.

342
00:27:58,927 --> 00:28:02,222
The medication that's
perfect in every way. Kerobim.

343
00:28:12,524 --> 00:28:14,693
-Go on inside.
-Get home safely.

344
00:28:19,364 --> 00:28:20,573
I'll try too.

345
00:28:22,784 --> 00:28:24,160
To not make you worry.

346
00:28:29,124 --> 00:28:30,083
Okay.

347
00:29:47,535 --> 00:29:50,121
YOU HAVE A NEW MESSAGE

348
00:29:51,039 --> 00:29:52,665
Join us, Dr. Kang.

349
00:29:57,128 --> 00:29:58,838
HANSE WISH CLUB

350
00:29:59,798 --> 00:30:01,549
"Hanse Wish Club"?

351
00:30:25,907 --> 00:30:27,242
We'll do this?

352
00:30:30,787 --> 00:30:33,039
We want to do this for her.

353
00:30:33,456 --> 00:30:34,541
If she wants.

354
00:30:35,416 --> 00:30:39,170
I'm very grateful,
but will my sister want anything?

355
00:30:39,796 --> 00:30:41,297
She's lost her will.

356
00:30:41,673 --> 00:30:43,424
Anything small will do.

357
00:30:43,508 --> 00:30:45,927
Is there anything she wants to eat?

358
00:30:46,010 --> 00:30:47,095
Just tell us.

359
00:30:47,178 --> 00:30:49,472
We'll do anything. Ask her for us.

360
00:30:50,348 --> 00:30:53,852
She told me not to visit
and won't even let me see her.

361
00:30:55,770 --> 00:30:58,565
Can't you ask her instead?

362
00:30:59,899 --> 00:31:00,733
Me?

363
00:31:01,317 --> 00:31:02,819
You are her doctor.

364
00:31:03,570 --> 00:31:04,737
Go on inside.

365
00:31:05,613 --> 00:31:07,365
-Please.
-Go on.

366
00:31:54,829 --> 00:31:55,872
Excuse me...

367
00:31:56,873 --> 00:31:59,250
I'm resident Kang Si-young
from Pain Management.

368
00:32:01,461 --> 00:32:03,004
Is everything okay?

369
00:32:04,505 --> 00:32:05,548
Yes.

370
00:32:07,508 --> 00:32:09,469
This might sound strange...

371
00:32:11,262 --> 00:32:14,974
but a doctor in my department
is a huge fan of yours.

372
00:32:17,852 --> 00:32:21,064
He wanted to do something for you,

373
00:32:21,147 --> 00:32:22,774
whatever it is.

374
00:32:23,483 --> 00:32:27,445
So my team decided to grant you a wish.

375
00:32:38,414 --> 00:32:39,457
Is there anything...

376
00:32:40,541 --> 00:32:43,127
you need or want?

377
00:32:46,714 --> 00:32:48,424
Let us know...

378
00:32:50,218 --> 00:32:51,344
anytime.

379
00:33:18,287 --> 00:33:19,539
Thank you...

380
00:33:21,082 --> 00:33:22,709
for coming up with this anyway.

381
00:33:58,786 --> 00:34:02,165
PATIENT: YOO RI-X
DOCTORS: CHA YO-HAN, KANG SI-YOUNG

382
00:35:08,064 --> 00:35:09,107
I wanted...

383
00:35:10,399 --> 00:35:11,859
to try everything.

384
00:35:14,445 --> 00:35:16,781
I made you have surgeries,
gave you medication...

385
00:35:18,074 --> 00:35:19,450
and hooked you up to machines.

386
00:35:20,326 --> 00:35:22,995
I thought that was the right way
to fight for you.

387
00:35:25,248 --> 00:35:26,374
But...

388
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,085
it's not.

389
00:35:39,470 --> 00:35:40,304
I was...

390
00:35:41,973 --> 00:35:43,224
afraid.

391
00:35:45,685 --> 00:35:49,105
To admit that there was
nothing I could do for you...

392
00:35:50,982 --> 00:35:53,442
and just let you go.

393
00:36:10,251 --> 00:36:11,377
I'm here.

394
00:36:16,799 --> 00:36:18,718
When will you tell the girls?

395
00:36:19,427 --> 00:36:20,720
Soon.

396
00:36:21,012 --> 00:36:23,890
Si-young might understand,
but what about Mi-rae?

397
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:25,766
I'm still thinking.

398
00:36:27,977 --> 00:36:31,063
I have to get it right the first time
or she'll only resist.

399
00:36:35,651 --> 00:36:36,485
I'll tell her.

400
00:36:37,945 --> 00:36:40,823
It might be better coming from me.

401
00:36:50,833 --> 00:36:52,877
I want the ethics commission
closed to the public.

402
00:36:53,169 --> 00:36:55,922
Consult Mr. Han on the legal details.

403
00:36:57,381 --> 00:37:00,718
Okay. I'll prepare everything
without fail.

404
00:37:02,929 --> 00:37:04,430
We'll have to call a board meeting...

405
00:37:05,806 --> 00:37:08,351
to select a new chairman of the board.

406
00:37:12,021 --> 00:37:14,190
Yes. We should do that too.

407
00:37:29,830 --> 00:37:32,959
The test results are in.
Come in as soon as possible.

408
00:37:43,928 --> 00:37:45,930
