00:37:55,231 --> 00:37:56,148
Dr. Cha!

411
00:38:04,282 --> 00:38:05,616
I drove here.

412
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:08,661
You can't drive yet,
so I'll take you to work.

413
00:38:14,292 --> 00:38:15,626
It's been sitting for a few years.

414
00:38:16,252 --> 00:38:18,170
There were no problems on the way here.

415
00:38:18,379 --> 00:38:20,464
Are you sure there were no problems?

416
00:38:26,304 --> 00:38:27,555
No wonder everything was blurry.

