00:38:39,233 --> 00:38:40,151
Dr. Cha.

419
00:38:44,447 --> 00:38:45,656
Dr. Cha!

420
00:38:46,699 --> 00:38:47,616
Dr. Cha.

421
00:38:50,786 --> 00:38:51,620
Help me!

422
00:39:00,963 --> 00:39:02,548
There. We can go now.

423
00:39:03,049 --> 00:39:05,551
-Okay.
-To Gyeongseo University Hospital.

424
00:39:05,634 --> 00:39:06,886
My test results are in.

425
00:39:11,349 --> 00:39:13,100
I haven't heard them yet.

426
00:39:13,351 --> 00:39:14,685
Will you keep giving me that look?

427
00:39:16,437 --> 00:39:17,646
Let's get going.

428
00:39:21,192 --> 00:39:23,194
Chopin in the morning. Nice.

429
00:39:30,785 --> 00:39:33,329
-Watch the curve.
-I'm a good driver.

430
00:39:43,047 --> 00:39:45,424
Dr. Lee's in charge
of the outpatients this morning.

431
00:39:45,549 --> 00:39:46,801
Work hard.

432
00:39:46,884 --> 00:39:48,177
Can I come with you?

433
00:39:48,552 --> 00:39:49,595
No.

434
00:39:52,681 --> 00:39:55,434
See you later. Drive safely.

435
00:39:55,518 --> 00:39:57,353
Don't turn on wipers
instead of the blinkers.

436
00:40:22,503 --> 00:40:24,672
-What's this for?
-Take it.

437
00:40:24,755 --> 00:40:26,632
You called me over this early
to give me this?

438
00:40:26,966 --> 00:40:29,427
I called you to feed you breakfast.

439
00:40:29,718 --> 00:40:31,720
Who keeps a talisman these days?

440
00:40:32,138 --> 00:40:35,724
I've been having weird dreams lately.

441
00:40:36,016 --> 00:40:39,728
Keep it safe
and be extra cautious at all times.

442
00:40:40,855 --> 00:40:41,897
You're helpless.

443
00:40:42,314 --> 00:40:43,941
-Are you done?
-Yes. I'm leaving.

444
00:40:44,066 --> 00:40:47,445
Hey, you have to be careful, okay?

445
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,405
Bye.

