463
00:41:40,998 --> 00:41:42,208
Dr. Heo!

464
00:41:44,668 --> 00:41:45,503
Yes?

465
00:41:46,128 --> 00:41:47,838
I'll keep the center under control.

466
00:41:48,297 --> 00:41:50,174
You do what you can do.

467
00:42:01,602 --> 00:42:04,772
What should we do then?

468
00:42:16,116 --> 00:42:19,620
Hello, I'm Kang Si-young, a resident
in Pain Management.

469
00:42:19,995 --> 00:42:20,829
I'm Kang Mi-rae.

470
00:42:21,330 --> 00:42:22,790
We brought some flowers.

471
00:42:23,624 --> 00:42:26,418
We thought your room seemed a little bare.

472
00:42:26,502 --> 00:42:29,296
They're fake flowers,
since we don't allow real ones.

473
00:42:29,380 --> 00:42:30,589
We brought a teddy bear too.

474
00:42:30,923 --> 00:42:32,383
We'll put it at your bedside.

475
00:42:41,392 --> 00:42:43,727
HANSE WISH CLUB

476
00:42:45,312 --> 00:42:46,814
Thank you, doctors.

477
00:42:50,192 --> 00:42:53,153
If you don't mind, can I ask for a favor?

478
00:42:54,405 --> 00:42:56,782
-Sure you can.
-Would you mind?

479
00:42:58,075 --> 00:42:59,660
If I wear lipstick,

480
00:43:00,160 --> 00:43:02,663
maybe I'll look a little less scary.

481
00:43:03,664 --> 00:43:04,957
I'll put it on for you.

482
00:43:08,544 --> 00:43:09,712
I feel nervous.

483
00:43:30,024 --> 00:43:33,986
I thought it would be best if my son

484
00:43:34,236 --> 00:43:36,071
doesn't see what I look like.

485
00:43:37,740 --> 00:43:38,782
But...

486
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:41,827
I miss him so much.

487
00:43:54,632 --> 00:43:55,674
All finished.

488
00:43:56,508 --> 00:43:58,177
Now let's see your son.

489
00:44:06,310 --> 00:44:07,353
What?

490
00:44:08,228 --> 00:44:09,938
What do you mean, he's not coming?

491
00:44:10,648 --> 00:44:12,191
I just got a call.

492
00:44:12,775 --> 00:44:16,695
He said he won't go because
he's too scared to see his mom.

493
00:44:17,029 --> 00:44:18,489
So he really won't come?

494
00:44:18,614 --> 00:44:20,324
He might never get to see her again.

495
00:44:20,407 --> 00:44:21,700
I don't know...

496
00:44:27,122 --> 00:44:29,958
Ri-hye. Let me explain what happened.

497
00:44:30,042 --> 00:44:32,086
Ri-hye. Ri-hye.

498
00:44:32,169 --> 00:44:33,045
Ri-hye!

499
00:44:33,587 --> 00:44:36,465
Ri-hye. Ri-hye.

500
00:44:37,841 --> 00:44:40,302
Ri-hye. Ri-hye.

501
00:44:40,552 --> 00:44:42,137
Oh, no

